 for the library API.\\n\\n## Action taken\\n\\nRemoved the non-metadata failing generated test and its test-only support:\\n\\n- deleted `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/src/test/java/javax_activation/javax_activation_api/SecuritySupport2Test.java`\\n- deleted `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/src/test/resources/META-INF/mimetypes.default`\\n- removed the extra test-jar packaging block from `tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/build.gradle`\\n\\n## Why the remaining generated support should be preserved\\n\\nThe remaining generated support still covers meaningful native-image behaviors for this library and should stay in place:\\n\\n- `CommandInfoBeansTest` exercises `CommandInfo` instantiation through the Beans API.\\n- `MailcapCommandMapTest` exercises dynamic handler loading and fallback class loading paths.\\n- `SecuritySupport4Test` still validates resource enumeration through `SecuritySupport#getSystemResources`.\\n\\nThose tests represent real library behavior and were successful in the native run, so the remaining generated support is still useful and should be preserved.\"\n    },\n    \"metrics\": {\n      \"input_tokens_used\": 189482,\n      \"cached_input_tokens_used\": 1217792,\n      \"output_tokens_used\": 22133,\n      \"iterations\": 6,\n      \"cost_usd\": 0.6364,\n      \"generated_loc\": 150,\n      \"tested_library_loc\": 828,\n      \"metadata_entries\": 5,\n      \"code_coverage_percent\": 15.14\n    },\n    \"artifacts\": {\n      \"test_file\": \"tests/src/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/src/test/java/javax_activation/javax_activation_api/SecuritySupport4Test.java\",\n      \"metadata_file\": \"metadata/javax.activation/javax.activation-api/1.2.0/reachability-metadata.json\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-17T19:11:52.522884Z\",\n    \"library\": \"javax.activation:javax.activation-api:1.2.0\",\n    \"starting_commit\": \"a7a7a583f2a0f9ec9bf201e26e30e9