namicAccess\": {\n        \"breakdown\": {\n          \"reflection\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 3,\n            \"totalCalls\": 3\n          },\n          \"resources\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 2,\n            \"totalCalls\": 2\n          }\n        },\n        \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n        \"coveredCalls\": 5,\n        \"totalCalls\": 5\n      },\n      \"libraryCoverage\": {\n        \"instruction\": {\n          \"covered\": 168,\n          \"missed\": 19462,\n          \"ratio\": 0.008558,\n          \"total\": 19630\n        },\n        \"line\": {\n          \"covered\": 45,\n          \"missed\": 4796,\n          \"ratio\": 0.009296,\n          \"total\": 4841\n        },\n        \"method\": {\n          \"covered\": 5,\n          \"missed\": 1199,\n          \"ratio\": 0.004153,\n          \"total\": 1204\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"post_generation_intervention\": {\n      \"stage\": \"metadata_fix_failed\",\n      \"intervention_file\": \"post-gen-interventions/org.codehaus.woodstox_stax2-api_4.2.2.md\",\n      \"analysis_markdown\": \"# Post-generation intervention report\\n\\nLibrary: org.codehaus.woodstox:stax2-api:4.2.2\\nStage: `metadata_fix_failed`\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nBoth failing native tests had the same root cause: this was a metadata-related failure, not a bad test and not a native-image platform limitation. `XMLValidationSchemaFactory.newInstance(...)` looks up a custom service definition resource at `META-INF/services/org.codehaus.stax2.validation.XMLValidationSchemaFactory.dtd`. In the failing native image, that resource was not registered, so runtime lookup returned no provider and both tests failed with `FactoryConfigurationError`.\\n\\n## Failure breakdown\\n\\n### `loadsFactoryFromSystemResourcesWhenNoClassLoaderIsProvided()`\\n- **Root cause:** missing native-image resource metadata for `META-INF/services/org.codehaus.stax2.validation.XMLValidationSchemaFactory.dtd`\\n- **Why it failed:** the null-classloader path falls back to system resource lookup, but the service file was not embedded in the native image, so no `XMLValidationSchemaFactory` implementation could be found.\\n\\n### `loadsFactoryFromExplicitClassLoaderResources()`\\n- **Root cause:** same missing native-image resource metadata\\n- **Why it failed:** even with the explicit test class loader, the same service file was absent from the native image, so provider discovery failed in the same way.\\n\\n## Codex log findings\\n\\nThe Codex log shows this was already identified correctly as a metadata gap. Codex added a resource entry for:\\n\\n- `META-INF/services/org.codehaus.stax2.validation.XMLValidationSchemaFactory.dtd`\\n\\nwith condition:\\n\\n- `org.codehaus.stax2.validation.XMLValidationSchemaFactory`\\n\\nAfter that change, Codex reran `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.codehaus.woodstox:stax2-api:4.2.2 --stacktrace` and both native tests passed.\\n\\n## Remaining missing metadata\\n\\nNone. The log indicates the metadata issue was resolved by registering the service resource. There is no evidence of a remaining reflection or JNI gap behind this failure.\\n\\n## Intervention decision\\n\\n- **Did not remove any generated tests.**\\n- **Did not modify metadata files in this intervention.**\\n\\n## Why the remaining generated support should be preserved\\n\\nThe generated support is still valuable because it covers a real native-image compatibility requirement in `stax2-api`: runtime discovery of `XMLValidationSchemaFactory` implementations through a custom `META-INF/services/...dtd` resource. The generated test and its service file validate both lookup variants exercised by the API:\\n\\n- system-resource lookup when no class loader is provided\\n- explicit class-loader resource lookup\\n\\nRemoving that generated support would discard legitimate coverage for a real metadata requirement that Codex already fixed.\"\n    },\n    \"metrics\": {\n      \"input_tokens_used\": 31973,\n      \"cached_input_tokens_used\": 504448,\n      \"output_tokens_used\": 9224,\n      \"iterations\": 1,\n      \"cost_usd\": 0.2645,\n      \"generated_loc\": 111,\n      \"tested_library_loc\": 225,\n      \"metadata_entries\": 0,\n      \"code_coverage_percent\": 0.93\n    },\n    \"artifacts\": {\n      \"test_file\": \"tests/src/org.codehaus.woodstox/stax2-api/4.2.2/src/test/java/org_codehaus_woodstox/stax2_api/XMLValidationSchemaFactoryTest.java\",\n      \"metadata_file\": \"metadata/org.codehaus.woodstox/stax2-api/4.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-22T04:28:45.655179Z\",\n    \"library\": \"org.codehaus.woodstox:stax2-api:4.2.2\",\n    \"starting_commit\": \"a0939efe722438024ba7181862b76101d8e14e59\",\n    \"ending_commit\": \"6f9d4c39c2d56ad8b2bb60c2b4ae6ed1c2e5b130\",\n    \"strategy_name\": \"dynamic_access_main_sources_pi_gpt-5.4\",\n    \"agent\": \"pi\",\n    \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.4\",\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"version\": \"4.2.2\",\n      \"dynamicAccess\": {\n        \"breakdown\": {\n          \"reflection\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 3,\n            \"totalCalls\": 3\n          },\n          \"resources\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 2,\n            \"totalCalls\": 2\n          }\n        },\n        \"coverageRatio\": 1.0,\n        \"coveredCalls\": 5,\n        \"totalCalls\": 5\n      },\n      \"libraryCoverage\": {\n        \"instruction\": {\n          \"covered\": 168,\n          \"missed\": 19462,\n          \"ratio\": 0.008558,\n          \"total\": 19630\n        },\n        \"line\": {\n          \"covered\": 45,\n          \"missed\": 4796,\n          \"ratio\": 0.009296,\n          \"total\": 4841\n        },\n        \"method\": {\n          \"covered\": 5,\n          \"missed\": 1199,\n          \"ratio\": 0.004153,\n          \"total\": 1204\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"metrics\": {\n      \"input_tokens_used\": 42152,\n      \"cached_input_tokens_used\": 487552,\n      \"output_tokens_used\": 8133,\n      \"iterations\": 1,\n      \"cost_usd\": 0.2439,\n      \"generated_loc\": 112,\n      \"tested_library_loc\": 45,\n      \"metadata_entries\": 0,\n      \"code_coverage_percent\": 0.93\n    },\n    \"artifacts\": {\n      \"test_file\": \"tests/src/org.codehaus.woodstox/stax2-api/4.2.2/src/test/java/org_codehaus_woodstox/stax2_api/XMLValidationSchemaFactoryTest.java\",\n      \"metadata_file\": \"metadata/org.codehaus.woodstox/stax2-api/4.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-22T01:36:55.212174Z\",\n    \"library\": \"org.conscrypt:conscrypt-openjdk-uber:2.0.0\",\n    \"starting_commit\": \"d54247dcf95d221b5f34ca4d06ea4fc5c488d750\",\n    \"ending_commit\": \"585e65817d8c53d3dc8f81fbca2155f983a8047c\",\n    \"strategy_name\": \"optimistic_dynamic_access_iterative_pi_gpt-5.4\",\n    \"agent\": \"pi\",\n    \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.4\",\n    \"status\": \"success\",\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"version\": \"2.0.0\",\n      \"dynamicAccess\": {\n        \"breakdown\": {\n          \"reflection\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 0.735294,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 25,\n            \"totalCalls\": 34\n          },\n          \"resources\": {\n            \"coverageRatio\": 0.5,\n            \"coveredCalls\": 2,\n            \"totalCalls\": 4\n          }\n        },\n        \"coverageRatio\": 0.710526,\n        \"coveredCalls\": 27,\n        \"totalCalls\": 38\n      },\n      \"libraryCoverage\": {\n        \"instruction\": {\n          \"covered\": 10483,\n          \"missed\": 28273,\n          \"ratio\": 0.270487,\n          \"total\": 38756\n        },\n        \"line\": {\n          \"covered\": 2442,\n          \"missed\": 7100,\n          \"ratio\": 0.255921,\n          \"total\": 9542\n        },\n        \"method\": {\n     